<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">안내</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <div class="body-titlebox">
                <h4>인터넷익스플로러(IE) 지원 종료 안내</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="body-contentbox">
                <p>인터넷익스플로러(IE) 서비스 지원이 2022년 6월 15일 종료됨에 따라 안전하고 원할한.......</p>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" onclick="popupClose();">오늘 하루그만보기</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script>
        const myModal = new bootstrap.Modal('#exampleModal');
        //ejs 변수 popup을 이용해서 모달 열지말지 결정.
        if( "<%=popup%>" !== "none") myModal.show();

        function popupClose(){
            axios({
                method: 'post',
                url: "/setpopup"
            }).then(()=>{
                myModal.hide();
                //modal hide
            })
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>